Use the following steps to initiate refund for activation fees:
-From the menu on the top left corner.
-Go to wallet
-Click on ‘Refund Activation Fees’ and type the description
- Submit
It will take up to 24 hours to refund your activation fees from our end and it might take 2 to 7 business days to reflect in your account.
Please ensure about following before raising the ticket:
1. You should not have any active rentals
2. You should not have any negative balance in PlugO Wallet
